creature-cli (2.15.6) unstable; urgency=medium

  * creature-mqtt: add Origin header and richer upgrade-failure logging for Linux NIO websocket handshake diagnostics.
  * creature-mqtt: expose --debug flag for verbose runs; bump version to trigger package update.
  * creature-cli + creature-mqtt: bump version to 2.15.6.

 -- April White <april@creature.engineering>  Thu, 11 Dec 2025 20:28:30 -0800

creature-cli (2.15.5) unstable; urgency=medium

  * creature-mqtt: swap Linux websocket client to NIO, add upgrade/error logging, and a --debug flag for verbose runs.
  * creature-mqtt: log offending websocket payloads when JSON decoding fails.
  * creature-cli + creature-mqtt: bump version to 2.15.5.

 -- April White <april@creature.engineering>  Thu, 11 Dec 2025 20:10:00 -0800

creature-cli (2.15.4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * creature-mqtt: replace URLSession websocket on Linux with NIO-based client to stop epoll spin / 100% CPU.
  * creature-mqtt: log offending websocket payload when JSON decoding fails for easier server debugging.
  * creature-cli + creature-mqtt: bump version to 2.15.4.

 -- April White <april@creature.engineering>  Thu, 11 Dec 2025 19:20:00 -0800

